metadata.name: Level Up!!!
metadata.description:
This is Ned.

As the final boss fell, and the credits started rolling, Ned reflected on his adventure...

He started with nothing.  
He overcame hurdles, accomplished missions and continually built on experience.  
The game got easier as he learnt more (albeit the odd psychotic boss here and there).  
He reached the end game, rich in knowledge and standing shoulder-to-shoulder with the companions he befriended along the way.

"We don't all make it to Level 88", thought Ned, "...but that's the game of life, I guess."

Originally created for the Sotheby's auction: Oddly Satisfying.
